    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Evaluate for tenderness, fluctuance\nLabs\nCBC- can have significant bleeding into the lesion, watch Hb\nImaging\nMRI is modality of choice for evaluation, but these lesions are also visible on CT\nUltrasound can show a fluid collection, but can't be used to rule out",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
    },
    "Management": {
      "text": "Will require surgical consultation and drainage",
      "subsections": {},
